SELECT u.user_id, u.username, a.access_time, al.level_name FROM users u LEFT JOIN access_logs a ON u.user_id = a.user_id LEFT JOIN access_levels al ON u.fingerprint_data = al.level_name ORDER BY a.access_time ASC LIMIT 5;

SELECT u.username, al.level_name FROM users u INNER JOIN user_permissions up ON u.user_id = up.user_id INNER JOIN access_levels al ON up.access_level = al.level_id WHERE up.access_level > 2 ORDER BY u.username DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT * FROM FingerprintUsers;

SELECT u.username, p.permission_name FROM FingerprintUsers u JOIN UserPermissions up ON u.id = up.user_id JOIN Permissions p ON up.permission_id = p.permission_id;
SELECT u.username, al.level_name FROM FingerprintUsers u LEFT JOIN UserAccessLevels ual ON u.id = ual.user_id LEFT JOIN AccessLevels al ON ual.level_id = al.level_id WHERE u.username LIKE '%a%';

SELECT u.username, p.permission_name, al.level_name FROM FingerprintUsers u JOIN UserPermissions up ON u.id = up.user_id JOIN Permissions p ON up.permission_id = p.permission_id JOIN UserAccessLevels ual ON u.id = ual.user_id JOIN AccessLevels al ON ual.level_id = al.level_id ORDER BY u.username ASC, p.permission_name DESC;
